    public interface IProxyTest
extends junit.framework.Test
    A Test that holds a reference to a delegate. Normally the delegate will extend TestCase to provide, possibly persistent, implementation specific logic for establishing test fixtures. The delegate is normally an instance of your concrete implementation specific test harness with access to any required configuration data, e.g., a properties file.
